Expand $(x+10)(2y+10)$. ||| We apply the distributive property repeatedly:

\begin{align*}
(x+10)(2y+10) &= x(2y+10) + 10(2y+10)\\
&= x\cdot 2y + x\cdot 10 + 10\cdot 2y + 10\cdot 10\\
