$i^{16} = i^{4*4} = 1$;
$i^{21} = i^{4*5 + 1} = i$;
$i^{26} = i^{4*6 + 2} = i^2 = -1$;
$i^{31} = i^{4*7 + 3} = i^3 = -i$.

Adding these values together, we get:
$$i^{11} + i^{16} + i^{21} + i^{26} + i^{31} = -i + 1 + i - 1 - i = -i.$$
